== 發行 ==
電影定於2016年10月14日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Warner Bros. Shifts Release Dates For ‘The Accountant’, ‘Going In Style’& ‘The House’|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-accountant-going-in-style-the-house-release-date-changes-1201716752/|accessdate=2016-03-10|work=Deadline|date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310110518/http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-accountant-going-in-style-the-house-release-date-changes-1201716752/|archive-date=2016-03-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]將電影排於2016年10月7日上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hayden|first1=Erik|title=Ben Affleck's 'Accountant' and 'Live By Night' Pushed Back by Warner Bros.|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ben-afflecks-accountant-live-by-813862|accessdate=2015-08-10|work=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2015-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810001543/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/ben-afflecks-accountant-live-by-813862|archive-date=2015-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更早之前的上映日為2016年1月29日<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Ben Affleck’s ‘The Accountant’Set for Jan. 29|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/the-accountant-release-date-ben-affleck-1201501076/|accessdate=2015-05-23|work=variety.com|date=2015-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523014750/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/the-accountant-release-date-ben-affleck-1201501076/|archive-date=2015-05-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《會計師》於國和加拿大的票房總收入為$8,630萬美元，而其他國家則賺得$6,890萬美元，全球總計合共$1.552億美元，對比其生產預算的$4,400萬美元<ref name=BOM />。

在美國，《會計師》跟《[[鋼鐵麥斯|鋼鐵麥斯]]》及《{{link-en|凱文哈特之現在是怎樣|Kevin Hart: What Now?}}》同期上映，並預期於開畫周末能從3,332間戲院中獲得$2,000萬至$2,500萬美元的票房，儘管電影工作室保守預算為$1,500萬美元<ref name=preview>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20161011-snap-story.html |title=Ben Affleck's 'The Accountant' is expected to unseat 'Girl On the Train' in slow box office weekend |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |access-date=2016-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013104058/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-movie-projector-20161011-snap-story.html |archive-date=2016-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在美國，電影於週四晚上的預覽獲得$135萬美元的票房收入，高於[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]主演的2014年電影《[[消失的爱人_(2014年电影)|失蹤罪]]》的$120萬美元。電影於開畫首天賺得$910萬美元，及開畫周末賺得$2,470萬美元，位居當周票房冠軍，亦是繼《失蹤罪》後，成為了艾佛列的職業生涯中所主演第二高的首演驚悚片（$3,750萬美元）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/weekend-box-office-the-accountant-kevin-hart-what-now-girl-on-the-train-1201836388/ |title=‘The Accountant’Calculates $24.7M Opening; ‘Max Steel’Rusts |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |access-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017171230/http://deadline.com/2016/10/weekend-box-office-the-accountant-kevin-hart-what-now-girl-on-the-train-1201836388/ |archive-date=2016-10-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在上映的第二個周末，電影的票房賺得$1,360萬美元（下降了44.8％），票房排名第四位<ref name="Prev">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/weekend-box-office-jack-reacher-tom-cruise-keeping-up-with-the-joneses-ouija-madea-tyler-perry-1201840348/|title=‘Madea’ To Push Well Past $27M As ‘Jack Reacher’ Takes $22M to $23M; ‘Joneses’ Can’t Keep Up – Sun. AM Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=October 23, 2016|accessdate=October 23, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610015323/https://deadline.com/2016/10/weekend-box-office-jack-reacher-tom-cruise-keeping-up-with-the-joneses-ouija-madea-tyler-perry-1201840348/|archive-date=2019-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

