=== 評價 ===
《會計師》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。根據[[匯總媒體|匯總媒體]]《[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]》網站，根據272個評論，持有51%的新鮮度，平均得分為5.66/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_accountant_2016 |title=The Accountant (2016) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2016-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013215013/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_accountant_2016 |archive-date=2016-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該網站的關鍵共識寫道：「《會計師》一口氣寫成了[[本·阿弗莱克|賓·艾佛力]]堅定的表現，一系列輕率的扣減讓觀眾留下一個漫無目的之動作驚悚片的困擾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_accountant_2016 |title=The Accountant (2016) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango_(company)|Fandango]] |accessdate=August 22, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013215026/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_accountant_2016 |archive-date=2016-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」。在《[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]》上，它有一個標準化的評級，電影根據45個評論，平均得分為51分（滿分100分），表示「好壞參半」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-accountant|title=The Accountant reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014042610/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-accountant|archive-date=2016-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-accountant|title=The Accountant Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=November 8, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014042610/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-accountant|archive-date=2016-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據《[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]》的觀眾投票，在A+至F之間的等級中，電影得到「A」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |access-date=2019-10-15 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20170916153548/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |archive-date=2017-09-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cu0es69VYAIdNw-.jpg |title=CinemaScore Grades |work=[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]] |via=[[Twitter|Twitter]] |access-date=2019-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409174630/https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cu0es69VYAIdNw-.jpg |archive-date=2017-04-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；而據《PostTrak》的報導，電影觀眾給它84％的正面評分，而當中的64％「明確推薦」<ref name=opening/>。

